* IPS70R1K4P7S SPICE Model for KiCad/Ngspice
* Based on Datasheet Rev 2.1 2018-02-13
* 700V CoolMOS P7 Power Transistor
* Fix: Removed inline comments and strictly formatted for Ngspice
*
* Pinout: 1=Gate, 2=Drain, 3=Source
*
.SUBCKT IPS70R1K4P7S 1 2 3

* VDMOS Model parameters
.MODEL CoolMOS_P7 VDMOS (
+ Vto=3.0
+ Kp=0.9
+ Phi=0.6
+ Rd=1.0
+ Rs=0.15
+ Rg=1.6
+ Cgs=155p
+ Cgdmax=100p
+ Cgdmin=3p
+ Bv=700
+ Ibv=1u
+ Is=10p
+ N=1.0
+ Tt=130n
+ Cjo=158p
+ Vj=0.9
)

* Instance of the model
M1 2 1 3 3 CoolMOS_P7

.ENDS IPS70R1K4P7S
